
Instructions for ‘Space Wars’


The Game—>

The idea of the game is to destroy the stormtroopers and Sith lords that are attacking your home planet. There are 4 levels to complete and it is up to your character, the last Jedi in the galaxy, to defeat them.

Controls—>

Spacebar - This allows the player to fire green, lightsaber type missiles to try and destroy the aliens and win the game. You can hold this down for a burst fire or tap it to gain a single shot.
          - Spacebar also starts the game and restarts it when you win/lose.

Left Arrow - This allows the player to move left across the canvas until you reach the edge of the game parameter and must move right.

Right Arrow - This allows the player to move right across the canvas until you reach the edge of the game parameter and must move left.